data.description:
Experience lakefront living at its best with this remarkable property boasting 52 feet of sandy shoreline on Dutch Lake! Embrace the summer vibes with easy access to your dock, thanks to a level walkway. The three-car garage, recently resurfaced and equipped with an additional workshop/storage space, accommodates both vehicles and lake essentials. The two-story floorplan opens up on the main level, inviting you to bask in panoramic lake views.
The kitchen has been tastefully updated with granite countertops, new flooring, stainless steel
appliances, knockdown ceilings, a new gas fireplace, and recessed lighting. Perfect for entertaining, the built-in buffet adds a touch of sophistication. The living room provides a picturesque view of Dutch Lake through new windows and offers convenient access to the lakeside yard via a side door. Almost all windows
have been replaced, enhancing the overall aesthetic and functionality of the home.
